entries.femaleVariant: That attack... in Paris... that was us?
Keep it down, will ya? That's classified.
I didn't sign up for this, man. Someone's gonna find out.
Whoever needs to know already knows. We keep our mouths shut, OK?
What did you think that extra seven per cent of the budget was for?
If this gets out, no fucking seven per cent's gonna save our asses!
How do you think it'll look? Supplying weapons for riots that our people started?
